Name: Endless Furry Killer 3D
About the game: Endless Furry Killer 3D is the second installment of the Furry Killer Series! The game is currently in alpha development process. DISCLAIMER: ENDLESS FURRY KILLER 3D DOES NOT CONDONE OR SUPPORT ANY TYPE OF REAL WORLD VIOLENCE OR HATE TOWARD ANY GROUP OF ANY KIND! Key Features: 1. Six Weapons, pistol, shotgun, mini-gun, rail-gun, and flamer. 2. Endless Furry combat. Play till you die! 3. Four ready to play levels. Easy, medium, and hard modes, and one test level. 4. Systems that keeps track of players score and time alive. 5. Hidden Easter Eggs! 6. Consistent updates!
